# Implementation Plan: Mobile Layout Optimization

Goal: Fix squeezed text and excessive padding on mobile devices, particularly visible in [CardCarousel](file:///c:/Workspace/petrobras-quest/src/components/aulas/shared.tsx#269-382) components and module containers. Ensure these fixes apply consistently across all lessons.

## User Review Required
No breaking changes. This is purely a CSS/Tailwind typography and spacing refinement targeted primarily at mobile screens (`< 768px`).

## Proposed Changes

### 1. [src/components/aulas/shared.tsx](file:///c:/Workspace/petrobras-quest/src/components/aulas/shared.tsx)
We will adjust the responsive paddings in key shared components used across multiple lessons.

#### [MODIFY] [CardCarousel](file:///c:/Workspace/petrobras-quest/src/components/aulas/shared.tsx#269-382)
- Reduce the padding of the `section` wrapper on mobile. Currently `p-6 md:p-8`, change to `p-4 md:p-8`.
- Reduce the padding of the individual cards on mobile. Currently `p-6 md:p-8 shadow-md`, change to `p-4 md:p-8 shadow-md`.
- Adjust the layout of the card content: Currently it uses `flex items-start gap-5`. On very small screens, the 14x14 icon takes up too much space. We will stack the icon and text vertically on mobile, or significantly reduce the gap and icon size on mobile.
- Adjust the `CarouselItem` padding.

#### [MODIFY] [ModuleSectionHeader](file:///c:/Workspace/petrobras-quest/src/components/aulas/shared.tsx#2912-3011)
- Ensure it doesn't have excessive bottom margin on mobile.

#### [MODIFY] [ModuleBanner](file:///c:/Workspace/petrobras-quest/src/components/aulas/shared.tsx#1264-1303)
- Ensure its internal padding isn't squeezing text on small screens.

### 2. General Container Adjustment (Example: [AulaCoesaoCoerencia.tsx](file:///c:/Workspace/petrobras-quest/src/components/aulas/portugues/AulaCoesaoCoerencia.tsx))
- Inspect the main `<section>` tags that wrap [ModuleSectionHeader](file:///c:/Workspace/petrobras-quest/src/components/aulas/shared.tsx#2912-3011) and [CardCarousel](file:///c:/Workspace/petrobras-quest/src/components/aulas/shared.tsx#269-382) inside specific lessons. Many use `p-8 md:p-10`. These should be updated to `p-4 md:p-10` or `p-5 md:p-10` to reclaim horizontal space on mobile.

## Verification Plan

### Manual Verification
1. Launch the application in a mobile viewport (e.g., iPhone 13 Pro width 390px).
2. Navigate to "Coesão e Coerência" -> Módulo 3.
3. Verify that the "Comunicados Oficiais" text inside the [CardCarousel](file:///c:/Workspace/petrobras-quest/src/components/aulas/shared.tsx#269-382) is no longer squeezed.
4. Navigate through other modules in the same lesson to ensure consistent spacing.
5. Check other lessons (e.g., "Concordância", "Crase") to confirm the shared component changes positively affect them without unintended side effects.
